ell as the Xbox 360 and PlayStation 3 consoles, and is backwards compatible on the Xbox One console.', 'Game Title.', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '116-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-04-14 13:26:29', '2019-04-14 13:26:29', '', 116, 'http://localhost/gaming_blog/?p=532', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
